Paris Saint-Germain striker Zlatan Ibrahimovic has been banned for four matches . 
  Ibrahimovic lost his temper during his side's defeat against Bordeaux on March 15 . 
  He insulted referee Lionel Jaffredo and used an expletive to describe France . 
  The Swede will miss PSG's matches against Nice, Lille, Metz and Nantes . 
 